For instance, if the score of (\textit{workInstitution{{2305.05403_FO0109||FO}}}, academicStaff) is greater than that of (academicStaff, \textit{workInstitution{{2305.05403_FO0110||FO}}}), then an entity with the enumerating predicate \textit{workInstitution{{2305.05403_FO0111||FO}}} is more likely to have the counting predicate academicStaff than the other way around.